"seconds for <guilabel>Kid Mode</guilabel> and 2 tenths of seconds for "
"<guilabel>Grown-up Mode</guilabel>. Increasing the time leaves you more time "
"to see your errors."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Taimer</guilabel>i seadistustedialoogil "
